Transaction starts
 → lock row
 → increment value
 → save contact
 → commit


✅ Repository SHOULD
        Fetch / save data
❌ Repository SHOULD NOT
        Contain business logic



✅ Service SHOULD
        Handle business rules
        Handle transactions
        Decide what happens
❌ Service SHOULD NOT
        Parse JSON
        Handle HTTP objects



✅ Controller SHOULD
        Accept DTO
        Call service
        Return DTO
❌ Controller SHOULD NOT
        Generate IDs
        Call repositories
        Contain business logic



Golden rule (memorize this)
If a transactional method catches a RuntimeException,
the transaction is already dead.





